<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Minutes"></a> Minutes </span></h2>
<p />
Key Initiatives <ol>
<li> User environment: goal to make all XSEDE modules available (currently 97 software modules installed); improving "tutorial command" and Connect client.
</li> <li> Distributed data caching service for OSG Connect Stash; distribution based on xrootd.
</li></ol> 
<p />
Top Issues / Concerns <ol>
<li> Preparing for the Software Carpentry workshop
</li> <li> Connect client: may require splitting BOSCO up
</li></ol> 
<p />
Key Accomplishments <ol>
<li> Integrated <span class="twikiNewLink">OrangeGrid<a href="/bin/edit/Management/OrangeGrid?topicparent=Management.20150107AgendaMinutes" rel="nofollow" title="OrangeGrid (this topic does not yet exist; you can create it)">?</a></span> with OSG Connect
</li> <li> Software Carpentry + OSG Connect bootcamp in Dec at UChicago.
</li> <li> Covered OSG Connect  at the ACI-REF webinar
</li></ol> 
